title: Discover Parramatta’s connected past and emerging future
description: Discover Parramatta North's remarkable history on Heritage Day - Saturday 24 May 2024 - with tours, fun family activities, live music, food and more.

title: Seeding grassroots for ‘The Green’ at Parramatta North
description: Today 'The Green' opened at Parramatta North, a revitalised 8,000 square metre sports ground for the local community.
